## Verification Plan

### Automated Checks
- The project must compile successfully without TypeScript errors `npm run build` or `npm run typecheck` inside `client/`.

### Manual Testing
- Log in and navigate to `/dashboard/settings`. Change the theme to `Midnight` and the accent to `Purple`, verifying that the entire application dynamically switches colors and re-renders successfully.
- Trigger RTL mode (Arabic) and confirm the sidebar correctly flips to the right side seamlessly, and table columns obey the directional alignment.
- Verify that standard flows (viewing reports, viewing performance stats) haven't fundamentally broken data fetching. 
